          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 64,
          "end": 77
        },
        "kind": "semantic",
        "text": "韓信曰乗人之車者載人之患衣人之衣者懐人之憂食人之食者死人之事",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "commentary-28",
        "range": {
